cc:Work.dc:title: Turkey, Scared Turkey...Happy Thanksgiving
cc:Work.dc:description:
A turkey with a hat gets frightened after seeing the cooked turkey on the table before him. He then imagines what took place for the cooked turkey to eventually be on the table. 
 
This partly a remix of OpenClipart.org art including both turkeys, the silhouette, and the comic cloud. The table, chairs, stools and firghtened expression of the turkey I created. 
 
If you are interested in seeing how to create art like this and other art found on openclipart.org, please visit www.SimpleTutorials.net.
